Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张间美香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢雾诚二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\c&HCFF4FF&\3c&H1D6FD1&\pos(543,111)\frz357.629}甘乐：而且一旦失踪就再也找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(443,227)\frz1.157\c&HFFFDE7&\3c&HB36E44&}田中太郎：真的假的…
