Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.98,0:22:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.85,0:22:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dollars
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.86,0:22:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要日常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我也有点将信将疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 请暂时帮我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尝试和别人不同的生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切将尽在我的掌握之中……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我……
